item.title: Projects
item.description: ShowTrackr ShowTrackr is an application for avid tv show lovers. It lets you exlore the latest tv shows, save them for later viewing and recommend your favorite tv shows to your close ones. This project is still in beta and done as a hobby to learn more advanced iOS development topics. Programmatic View and Layouts Dependency Injection UICollectionviewcompositionallayout Working with remote API Kingfisher Github: github.com/abatjarg/ShowTrackrProject Screenshots LearnByDoing LearnByDoing is a open source project to keep collection of sample application that helped me to learn iOS development.
